⚙️ Hadoop Cluster and Admin Commands

hadoop version – Show Hadoop version

start-dfs.sh – Start HDFS daemons (NameNode, DataNodes)

stop-dfs.sh – Stop HDFS daemons

start-yarn.sh – Start YARN daemons (ResourceManager, NodeManager)

stop-yarn.sh – Stop YARN daemons

hdfs dfsadmin -report – HDFS usage and live datanode status

hdfs dfsadmin -safemode get – Check safemode status

hdfs dfsadmin -safemode enter – Force safemode

hdfs dfsadmin -safemode leave – Leave safemode

hdfs dfsadmin -refreshNodes – Refresh the list of datanodes
